Paper: hep-th/9712120

Date: 1997-12-12

Title: Stokes Theorem for Loop Variables of Non-Abelian Gauge Field

Authors: M. Hirayama and S. Matsubara (Toyama University)

Comments: PTPTeX, 18 pages, add a reference

Journal-ref: Prog.Theor.Phys. 99 (1998) 691-706

A simple analytic proof of the formula known as the non-Abelian Stokestheorem is given. It is explicitly shown that the consistency of the formula isguaranteed by the Bianchi identity for the gauge field. An attempt is made toconstruct the Lagrangian for the gauge field in terms of loop variables.